                            <comment id="12693480" author="mikemccand" created="Sat, 28 Mar 2009 19:01:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attached patch.  I plan to commit in a day or two.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I added a new deprecated expert public method to IndexReader:&lt;br/&gt;
getFieldCacheWrapper().  Default impl is to return &quot;this&quot;, but&lt;br/&gt;
SegmentReader overrides that and returns a wrapper class that forwards&lt;br/&gt;
hashCode()/equals() to the underlying freqStream.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12693492" author="mikemccand" created="Sat, 28 Mar 2009 21:38:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;New patch.  The last one was causing entries in FieldCache to get booted too soon.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
